# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Production Environment Variables Template
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# Referência única: docs/ops/ENV_MATRIX.md (Stack 2026)
#
# Copy this file to .env.production and fill in the values
# SECURITY: Never commit .env.production; use Vercel env vars in production.
# Setup: cp .env.production.example .env.production && edit && vercel env add ...
#
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ━━━ REQUIRED: Supabase Core ━━━

# Supabase Project URL
# Where to find: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API
# Format: https://[project-ref].supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co

# Supabase Anon/Public Key
# Where to find: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API → anon/public
# Format: JWT (eyJ...) or project key (sup_pk_...). Do not commit the real key.
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ━━━ REQUIRED: API Configuration ━━━

# API Base URL — Production = Supabase Edge (Stack 2026). Local = gateway on 4320.
# Production: https://<PROJECT_REF>.supabase.co/functions/v1 (see docs/ops/MIGRATION_RENDER_TO_EDGE.md)
VITE_API_BASE=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co/functions/v1

# Internal API Token (for server-to-server communication)
# Where to find: Generate secure random string or use existing token
# Format: any secure string (minimum 32 characters recommended)
VITE_INTERNAL_API_TOKEN=chefiapp-internal-token-production-REPLACE-ME

# ━━━ OPTIONAL: Sentry Monitoring ━━━

# Sentry DSN (Data Source Name)
# Where to find: Sentry Dashboard → Settings → Projects → [Your Project] → Client Keys (DSN)
# Format: https://[public-key]@[org].ingest.sentry.io/[project-id]
# Required for: Error tracking, performance monitoring, session replay
# Setup: bash scripts/monitoring/setup-sentry.sh
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=https://examplePublicKey@o0.ingest.sentry.io/0000000

# Sentry Auth Token
# Where to find: Sentry Dashboard → Settings → Account → Auth Tokens → Create New Token
# Permissions needed: project:releases, project:write, org:read
# Required for: Sourcemap uploads, release tracking
VITE_SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=sntrys_EXAMPLE_TOKEN_REPLACE_ME

# Sentry Organization Slug
# Where to find: Sentry Dashboard URL → https://sentry.io/organizations/[org-slug]/
# Format: organization name in URL (lowercase, hyphenated)
VITE_SENTRY_ORG=your-organization

# Sentry Project Name
# Where to find: Sentry Dashboard → Project name
# Format: project name (lowercase, hyphenated)
VITE_SENTRY_PROJECT=merchant-portal

# ━━━ OPTIONAL: Payment Gateway (Stripe) ━━━

# Stripe Secret Key (for backend)
# Where to find: Stripe Dashboard → Developers → API keys → Secret key
# Format: sk_live_... (production) or sk_test_... (test mode)
# Used by: integration-gateway for payment processing
# NOTE: This is a backend variable, not VITE_ prefixed for security
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_EXAMPLE_REPLACE_ME

# Stripe Publishable Key (for frontend)
# Where to find: Stripe Dashboard → Developers → API keys → Publishable key
# Format: pk_live_... (production) or pk_test_... (test mode)
# Used by: merchant-portal checkout forms
VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_EXAMPLE_REPLACE_ME

# ━━━ OPTIONAL: Analytics ━━━

# Plausible Analytics Domain
# Where to find: Plausible Dashboard → Your domain
# Format: your-domain.com
VITE_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN=merchant.chefiapp.com

# Google Analytics Measurement ID
# Where to find: Google Analytics → Admin → Data Streams → Measurement ID
# Format: G-XXXXXXXXXX
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# ━━━ OPTIONAL: Feature Flags ━━━

# Enable/disable features in production
# Values: true or false

# Enable new payment flow
VITE_FEATURE_NEW_PAYMENT_FLOW=true

# Enable experimental features
VITE_FEATURE_EXPERIMENTAL=false

# Enable debug logging (DO NOT enable in production)
VITE_DEBUG_MODE=false

# ━━━ OPTIONAL: Custom Branding ━━━

# App Name (displayed in UI)
VITE_APP_NAME=ChéfiApp

# Support Email
VITE_SUPPORT_EMAIL=support@chefiapp.com

# Support Phone (WhatsApp)
VITE_SUPPORT_PHONE=+351912345678

# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Verification Checklist
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# Before deploying to production, verify:
#
# ✅ All REQUIRED variables are set with real values
# ✅ Supabase URL and key are from PRODUCTION project
# ✅ API Base URL points to production gateway
# ✅ Sentry configured for production monitoring
# ✅ No test/development credentials used
# ✅ .env.production is in .gitignore (NEVER commit)
# ✅ Variables synced to Vercel:
#    $ vercel env add VITE_SUPABASE_URL production
#    $ vercel env add VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY production --sensitive
#    $ vercel env add VITE_API_BASE production
#    (repeat for all variables)
#
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ━━━ Quick Setup Script ━━━
#
# Run this interactive setup:
#   $ bash scripts/monitoring/setup-sentry.sh
#
# Or manually set in Vercel:
#   $ vercel env add VITE_SUPABASE_URL production
#   $ vercel env add VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY production --sensitive
#   $ vercel env add VITE_API_BASE production
#   $ vercel env add VITE_INTERNAL_API_TOKEN production --sensitive
#   $ vercel env add VITE_SENTRY_DSN production --sensitive
#   $ vercel env add VITE_SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN production --sensitive
#   $ vercel env add VITE_SENTRY_ORG production
#   $ vercel env add VITE_SENTRY_PROJECT production
#
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
